    "text" : "<h1 style=\"text-align:center;\"> Практические примеры применения <code>enum</code></h1>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;\"> Сравнение порядковых номеров</h2>\n\n<p>Можно сравнивать<strong><code> enum</code></strong> через <strong><code>ordinal</code></strong>:</p>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum Size:\n  case Small, Medium, Large, XLarge\n\ndef compare(s1: Size, s2: Size): Int =\n  s1.ordinal - s2.ordinal\n\nprintln(compare(Size.Small, Size.Large))   // отрицательное\nprintln(compare(Size.Large, Size.Small))   // положительное\nprintln(compare(Size.Medium, Size.Medium)) // 0\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;\">Перебор значений</h2>\n\n<h3>Итерация по всем значениям:</h3>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum Day:\n  case Mon, Tue, Wed, Thu, Fri, Sat, Sun\n\nDay.values.foreach { day =&gt;\n  println(s\"$day: ordinal ${day.ordinal}\")\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>Фильтрация:</h3>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum Grade:\n  case A, B, C, D, F\n\nval passingGrades = Grade.values.filter(_.ordinal &lt; 4)\n// Array(A, B, C, D)\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>Поиск:</h3>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum State:\n  case Init, Running, Paused, Finished\n\nval running = State.values.find(_.ordinal == 1)\n// Some(Running)\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>Получение имен всех значений:</h3>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum Command:\n  case Start, Stop, Restart\n\nval names = Command.values.map(_.toString)\n// Array(\"Start\", \"Stop\", \"Restart\")\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;\">Моделирование направления</h2>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum Direction:\n  case North\n  case South\n  case East\n  case West\n\n// |Direction| = 4\n\ndef opposite(d: Direction): Direction = d match\n  case Direction.North =&gt; Direction.South\n  case Direction.South =&gt; Direction.North\n  case Direction.East  =&gt; Direction.West\n  case Direction.West  =&gt; Direction.East\n\ndef turnRight(d: Direction): Direction = d match\n  case Direction.North =&gt; Direction.East\n  case Direction.East  =&gt; Direction.South\n  case Direction.South =&gt; Direction.West\n  case Direction.West  =&gt; Direction.North\n\n// Проверка\nprintln(opposite(Direction.North))    // South\nprintln(turnRight(Direction.North))   // East</code></pre>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;\">HTTP методы</h2>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum HttpMethod:\n  case GET\n  case POST\n  case PUT\n  case DELETE\n  case PATCH\n\n// |HttpMethod| = 5\n\ndef isIdempotent(method: HttpMethod): Boolean = method match\n  case HttpMethod.GET | HttpMethod.PUT | HttpMethod.DELETE =&gt; true\n  case HttpMethod.POST | HttpMethod.PATCH =&gt; false\n\nprintln(isIdempotent(HttpMethod.GET))   // true\nprintln(isIdempotent(HttpMethod.POST))  // false</code></pre>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;\">Моделирование состояния процесса</h2>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum GameState:\n  case MainMenu\n  case Playing\n  case Paused\n  case GameOver\n\n// |GameState| = 4\n\ndef canSaveGame(state: GameState): Boolean = state match\n  case GameState.Playing =&gt; true\n  case GameState.Paused  =&gt; true\n  case GameState.MainMenu | GameState.GameOver =&gt; false</code></pre>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;\">Команда с параметром</h2>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum Command:\n  case Start\n  case Stop\n  case SetSpeed(value: Int)\n  case SetMode(mode: String)\n\ndef executeCommand(cmd: Command): Unit = cmd match\n  case Command.Start =&gt; println(\"Starting...\")\n  case Command.Stop =&gt; println(\"Stopping...\")\n  case Command.SetSpeed(v) =&gt; println(s\"Speed set to $v\")\n  case Command.SetMode(m) =&gt; println(s\"Mode changed to $m\")\n\n// Использование\nexecuteCommand(Command.Start)\nexecuteCommand(Command.SetSpeed(100))\nexecuteCommand(Command.SetMode(\"turbo\"))</code></pre>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;\">Токен авторизации</h2>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-scala\">enum AuthToken:\n  case Anonymous\n  case Bearer(token: String)\n  case ApiKey(key: String)\n\ndef getAuthHeader(token: AuthToken): Option[String] = token match\n  case AuthToken.Anonymous =&gt; None\n  case AuthToken.Bearer(t) =&gt; Some(s\"Bearer $t\")\n  case AuthToken.ApiKey(k) =&gt; Some(s\"X-API-Key: $k\")\n\n// Примеры\nprintln(getAuthHeader(AuthToken.Anonymous))           // None\nprintln(getAuthHeader(AuthToken.Bearer(\"abc123\")))    // Some(Bearer abc123)\nprintln(getAuthHeader(AuthToken.ApiKey(\"secret\")))    // Some(X-API-Key: secret)</code></pre>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;\"> </h2>",
